{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/spring/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>시작하기에 앞서</h2>\n<p>SpringFrameWork를 사용한지는 약 1년정도 되었지만, 개념에 대해서 다시 알아보고자 정리해봅니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>스프링이란?</h3>\n<p>스프링은 Java Enterprise Develop을 편하게 도와주는 <strong><code>오픈소스 경량급 프레임워크</code></strong> 입니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>스프링의 특징</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>IOC (Invertion Of Control)</code></strong> 제어 역전</li>\n<li><strong><code>DI (Dependecy Injection)</code></strong> 의존성 주입</li>\n<li><strong><code>AOP (Aspect-Oriented Programming)</code></strong> 관점 지향 프로그래밍</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>IOC ?</h3>\n<p>객체 생성 부터 Life Cycle까지 Object에 대한 제어권이 <strong><code>개발자가 아닌 FrameWork</code></strong> 에 존재한다는 의미입니다.</p>\n<p>예를 들어보자면,</p>\n<p>과거에는 의존관계를 개발자가 직접 제어했습니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"java\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">@</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">Repository</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">public</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">class</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-10 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">TestRepository</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">@</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">Service</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc